---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us — Resurgence Builds" description="Learn more about Resurgence Builds, a 100% ad-free passion project dedicated to The Division Resurgence.">
  <div class="container section content-width">
    <h1 class="heading-accent">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>Resurgence Builds</strong>. This site is a 100% ad-free passion project built by and for the community of <em>The Division Resurgence</em>.</p>
      
      <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
      <p>We got tired of scrolling through low-effort, copy-pasted SEO spam sites just to find out what the meta is for the Dark Zone. We wanted a clean, fast, and mathematically accurate database of the best builds in the game.</p>
      <p>So, we built it ourselves.</p>
      
      <h2>No Ads, No Paywalls, No Nonsense</h2>
      <p>You won't find any auto-playing video ads, pop-ups, or paywalls here. We believe in providing high-quality, deeply researched game knowledge without compromising the user experience. Our goal is simple: to be the definitive written resource for The Division Resurgence.</p>
      
      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>Have a build that's shredding the Dark Zone? Found a typo? Just want to tell us our Vanguard build is trash? We're always looking for feedback to keep the meta updated. Stay tuned for our upcoming Discord server.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
